{"tid":1539062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"扑輕鐵入閘機既手足留意","createTime":"2019-09-04T08:44:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T13:01:44.000Z","uid":120915,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d4e3a347647e39182ea1385f731cb562fd55eefe","tid":1539062,"uid":120915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:44:02.000Z","msg":"淨係唔小心整親個入閘機好啦，搞出閘機既話有啲人入咗閘冇得出會收貴咗架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n  仲要記得搞埋對面月台，今日見好多人特登走去對面月台拍入閘先再返原本個月台上車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n  搞掂埋個濕鳩cctv同售票機就可以返去訓了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b1a0ed66f8e1d488db59c05ae1294462a6efaec","tid":1539062,"uid":290815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:44:39.000Z","msg":"大家要到幾時先察覺，靠政府去實現五大訴求已經變成一個好恐怖既局？<br />\n<br />\n[時光倒流Re-post] 香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先大家可以選擇服用咗以上文章先<br />\n<br />\n然後我可以反問一句，有冇人諗過五大訴求真係實現既情況會係點？<br />\n<br />\n係，的確可能證實到瘋狂既民意係可以改變到政府所作出既決定，但下次兩地一檢呢？再下次智慧燈柱、全面普教中呢？反送中2.0、3.0發生，真係好？點解要跟住個垃圾政權條尾走？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔好再「<span style=\"color: red;\">要求</span>」政府畀到五個願望你哋，請大家一齊親手達成依五個，甚至一百個願望都得，可唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n睇唔明我講咩既話請讀上面篇文章一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"744ce2a2752b3ceeb228c6d5bb572840a76ccbfe","tid":1539062,"uid":204306,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:48:03.000Z","msg":"輕鐵本身都唔洗錢搭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"034e9394910564d87811875cbf40f17cdb551fc5","tid":1539062,"uid":120915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"744ce2a2752